subject: Baseball (College)
Football (College)
Shoplifting and Employee Theft (Retail)
lead_paragraph: The police said Jameis Winston, Florida State’s Heisman-winning quarterback, ordered $32.72 of crab legs and crawfish from a Publix but left without paying. His baseball coach suspended him.
